1
00:02:06,640 --> 00:02:07,920
What are you taking?

2
00:02:35,639 --> 00:02:37,120
You called me here just for this?

3
00:02:40,240 --> 00:02:41,039
Or what?

4
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:44,400
Because you love me?

5
00:03:38,080 --> 00:03:38,800
You think

6
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:39,960
we're even now?

7
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:48,439
Breakfast is ready.

8
00:06:50,199 --> 00:06:51,600
Today is the kick-off meeting

9
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:52,519
for the Phase II project,

10
00:06:52,839 --> 00:06:53,839
and it's also the day

11
00:06:53,839 --> 00:06:55,040
you start as the director's assistant.

12
00:06:57,399 --> 00:06:59,800
There's about

13
00:07:01,279 --> 00:07:01,920
30 minutes left.

14
00:07:04,959 --> 00:07:05,759
I'll go get changed.

15
00:07:12,839 --> 00:07:13,600
Today

16
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:16,199
is the official launch

17
00:07:16,839 --> 00:07:18,720
of Lan Yue Phase II Resort,

18
00:07:18,839 --> 00:07:20,120
Lan Yue Yunqi Secret Realm.

19
00:07:26,759 --> 00:07:28,720
This project is a crucial step

20
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:30,759
in our company's strategic plan,

21
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:32,720
a benchmark project.

22
00:07:33,519 --> 00:07:34,199
I know

23
00:07:34,519 --> 00:07:35,879
In the past few months,

24
00:07:36,079 --> 00:07:38,079
from planning to bidding,

25
00:07:38,319 --> 00:07:39,839
you've overcome many challenges.

26
00:07:39,879 --> 00:07:42,040
On behalf of Lan Yue,

27
00:07:42,199 --> 00:07:44,000
I'd like to extend my sincere thanks

28
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:45,480
to everyone involved in the project.

29
00:08:01,079 --> 00:08:01,800
Hello, miss.

30
00:08:01,800 --> 00:08:03,120
How can I help you?

31
00:08:03,519 --> 00:08:04,560
It's my first day at work,

32
00:08:04,639 --> 00:08:05,639
and I haven't received my work badge yet.

33
00:08:06,839 --> 00:08:08,800
Please register first.

34
00:08:09,319 --> 00:08:11,000
Let me check your name.

35
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:11,759
What's your name?

36
00:08:11,759 --> 00:08:12,399
Zhou Wan.

37
00:08:13,079 --> 00:08:14,199
Which Zhou?

38
00:08:15,079 --> 00:08:16,319
Zhou Wu Zheng Wang. [*A tongue twister in Chinese]

39
00:08:17,079 --> 00:08:17,720
And Wan?

40
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:23,000
Jun, why can't I find her?

41
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:23,959
I don't know.

42
00:08:23,959 --> 00:08:25,279
I'm new here too.

43
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:27,600
Please wait a moment.

44
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:28,720
In the future,

45
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:30,600
we will be driven by innovation,

46
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:32,639
customer needs,

47
00:08:32,840 --> 00:08:33,639
and work together

48
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:36,960
to embark on a journey

49
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:38,440
full of opportunities and challenges.

50
00:08:39,600 --> 00:08:42,360
Bravo!

51
00:08:43,919 --> 00:08:45,279
Now, let me introduce

52
00:08:45,279 --> 00:08:46,440
the core members

53
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:47,440
of our Phase II

54
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:48,399
project team.

55
00:08:53,919 --> 00:08:54,799
Sorry, sorry.

56
00:08:54,799 --> 00:08:56,159
I'm so sorry for being late.

57
00:09:01,639 --> 00:09:02,200
Come on.

58
00:09:03,919 --> 00:09:04,679
First,

59
00:09:04,679 --> 00:09:06,120
our project director,

60
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:07,399
Mr. Lu Xixiao,

61
00:09:07,679 --> 00:09:09,279
Young Master Lu.

62
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:16,080
Deputy Director and Director's Assistant,

63
00:09:16,080 --> 00:09:17,000
Ms. Zhou Wan.

64
00:09:21,879 --> 00:09:23,039
Hello, everyone. I'm Zhou Wan.

65
00:09:23,679 --> 00:09:25,960
Project Engineering Manager, Mr. Cheng Feng.

66
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:30,080
Excuse me.

67
00:09:30,919 --> 00:09:31,360
Mr. Lan.

68
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:37,240
To facilitate communication

69
00:09:37,240 --> 00:09:39,600
between Phase II and headquarters,

70
00:09:40,039 --> 00:09:42,000
the board has decided,

71
00:09:42,480 --> 00:09:44,440
in accordance with company policy,

72
00:09:44,840 --> 00:09:45,559
to appoint

73
00:09:45,960 --> 00:09:47,679
Mr. Jiang Yan, Strategic Director,

74
00:09:47,679 --> 00:09:49,159
to Phase II.

75
00:09:49,480 --> 00:09:50,279
Okay.

76
00:09:52,399 --> 00:09:54,279
Mr. Jiang

77
00:09:54,279 --> 00:09:56,639
graduated from Huaqing University of Science and Technology,

78
00:09:56,639 --> 00:09:57,720
and has worked

79
00:09:57,720 --> 00:09:59,600
for several well-known

80
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:00,799
property groups.

81
00:10:01,679 --> 00:10:02,960
I believe his joining

82
00:10:03,039 --> 00:10:04,440
will definitely give our Phase II project

83
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:05,960
a boost.

84
00:10:08,159 --> 00:10:08,960
Great!

85
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:18,879
Pleasure to work with you.

86
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:27,200
Looking forward to it.

87
00:10:30,039 --> 00:10:30,840
Okay.

88
00:10:47,320 --> 00:10:48,039
Come in.

89
00:10:49,759 --> 00:10:51,679
I'm glad to be your colleague.

90
00:10:54,639 --> 00:10:55,399
I didn't know

91
00:10:55,399 --> 00:10:57,080
you would join the Phase II Project.

92
00:10:58,000 --> 00:10:58,679
You...

93
00:10:59,519 --> 00:11:01,559
It was Mr. Lu's last-minute decision.

94
00:11:02,480 --> 00:11:03,799
I'm just following orders.

95
00:11:08,159 --> 00:11:09,440
Then I'll be relying on

96
00:11:09,679 --> 00:11:11,080
Director Jiang's guidance from now on.

97
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:16,320
Do you want to go home together after work?

98
00:11:18,039 --> 00:11:19,360
I have a lot of things to do.

99
00:11:19,559 --> 00:11:20,799
You can go home first after work.

100
00:11:20,799 --> 00:11:22,080
It doesn't matter. I'll wait for you.

101
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:23,960
It's better to take my car than to take a taxi.

102
00:11:26,120 --> 00:11:26,759
Jiang Yan

103
00:11:28,519 --> 00:11:29,720
I don't go home

104
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:32,240
recently.

105
00:11:33,559 --> 00:11:36,000
What do you mean?

106
00:11:39,759 --> 00:11:40,639
Zhou Wan

107
00:11:42,120 --> 00:11:42,840
Sorry.

108
00:11:48,440 --> 00:11:49,720
What's up, Director Lu?

109
00:11:51,879 --> 00:11:52,720
Are you free?

110
00:11:53,600 --> 00:11:54,639
If so,

111
00:11:56,240 --> 00:11:57,559
go make me a cup of coffee.

112
00:12:03,039 --> 00:12:04,039
Okay, Director Lu.

113
00:12:10,159 --> 00:12:11,919
Who is Director Jiang?

114
00:12:12,120 --> 00:12:13,120
He is handpicked by General Manager Lu

115
00:12:13,120 --> 00:12:14,039
to work in Lan Yue.

116
00:12:14,039 --> 00:12:15,320
Don't you understand the relationship?

117
00:12:15,519 --> 00:12:16,399
I don't get it.

118
00:12:16,799 --> 00:12:17,440
Mr. Lu is

119
00:12:17,440 --> 00:12:18,600
the son of General Manager Lu.

120
00:12:18,720 --> 00:12:19,960
General Manager Lan trusts Mr. Lu.

121
00:12:19,960 --> 00:12:21,559
Director Jiang is General Manager Lu's man.

122
00:12:21,679 --> 00:12:22,720
What a complicated

123
00:12:22,720 --> 00:12:24,159
family business drama!

124
00:12:24,279 --> 00:12:25,120
It's normal that you don't understand.

125
00:12:25,120 --> 00:12:26,519
There's a lot to it.

126
00:12:26,919 --> 00:12:27,840
I'm telling you.

127
00:12:27,840 --> 00:12:30,000
Zhou Wan is a tough cookie.

128
00:12:30,240 --> 00:12:30,960
She used to be

129
00:12:30,960 --> 00:12:32,320
the top lady at Boxing Construction.

130
00:12:32,519 --> 00:12:33,639
She fought with Dingshang

131
00:12:33,639 --> 00:12:34,799
like hell.

132
00:12:35,320 --> 00:12:36,559
Now she comes to Dingshang

133
00:12:36,559 --> 00:12:38,039
and clings to the leader's leg.

134
00:12:38,039 --> 00:12:39,360
She even became the deputy director.

135
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:41,159
She's really good at it.

136
00:12:41,320 --> 00:12:42,159
Oh my god.

137
00:12:42,919 --> 00:12:43,679
Are you working or not?

138
00:12:43,679 --> 00:12:44,480
What are you talking about?

139
00:12:46,759 --> 00:12:48,080
Are you all out of work?

140
00:12:58,879 --> 00:13:00,120
You should

141
00:13:01,120 --> 00:13:02,440
stop them

142
00:13:02,440 --> 00:13:03,559
when they gossip.

143
00:13:04,159 --> 00:13:05,200
I don't care

144
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:06,320
about that anymore.

145
00:13:06,519 --> 00:13:07,840
They don't pay me.

146
00:13:08,360 --> 00:13:09,240
I don't care.

147
00:13:13,120 --> 00:13:14,919
Director Lu, here's your coffee.

148
00:13:31,960 --> 00:13:33,240
What do you want to eat? I'll cook for you.

149
00:13:35,000 --> 00:13:35,799
Whatever.

150
00:13:37,360 --> 00:13:39,039
I can't cook anything if you say so.

151
00:13:42,399 --> 00:13:43,039
Can you cook

152
00:13:43,039 --> 00:13:44,120
whatever I want?

153
00:13:46,240 --> 00:13:46,879
Fine.

154
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:49,080
I want Fotiaoqiang,

155
00:13:49,559 --> 00:13:50,320
Dongpo pork,

156
00:13:50,919 --> 00:13:52,200
Beef Wellington,

157
00:13:52,639 --> 00:13:53,679
Spanish fried rice,

158
00:13:53,679 --> 00:13:54,879
and Beef Bourguignon.

159
00:13:55,679 --> 00:13:57,000
Just cook whatever you want.

160
00:14:01,600 --> 00:14:02,440
I'm sorry.

161
00:14:03,480 --> 00:14:04,720
There's nothing at home.

162
00:14:11,080 --> 00:14:12,519
You can only eat noodles today.

163
00:14:13,559 --> 00:14:14,559
Next time I go to the supermarket,

164
00:14:14,559 --> 00:14:15,720
I'll buy some ingredients

165
00:14:15,840 --> 00:14:16,799
and make you a big meal.

166
00:14:49,360 --> 00:14:51,000
Beef Wellington,

167
00:14:51,000 --> 00:14:52,799
Buddha jumps over the wall,

168
00:14:52,919 --> 00:14:53,720
and everything else are all here.

169
00:14:54,480 --> 00:14:55,120
Eat up.

170
00:14:56,720 --> 00:14:57,559
Where are the chopsticks?

171
00:15:07,559 --> 00:15:08,720
Unwashed chopsticks.

172
00:15:12,559 --> 00:15:13,120
Wait a minute.

173
00:15:14,399 --> 00:15:16,159
I'll add some expired scallions.

174
00:15:19,039 --> 00:15:20,000
It won't be tasty.

175
00:15:20,919 --> 00:15:22,080
You think I won't dare to eat it?

176
00:15:22,200 --> 00:15:22,879
Eat.

177
00:15:26,480 --> 00:15:27,279
I'll eat.

178
00:15:37,879 --> 00:15:38,679
It's not tasty.

179
00:15:40,879 --> 00:15:42,320
I told you it wouldn't be tasty.

180
00:15:46,240 --> 00:15:47,080
What happened to your hand?

181
00:15:49,720 --> 00:15:51,080
Cooking for you.

182
00:15:51,879 --> 00:15:52,919
It burned me.

183
00:15:57,039 --> 00:15:58,440
I never got burned

184
00:15:58,440 --> 00:15:59,720
when I worked in college.

185
00:16:00,240 --> 00:16:02,080
But I got hurt here.

186
00:16:04,120 --> 00:16:05,159
You worked?

187
00:16:06,759 --> 00:16:08,080
Who else would support me?

188
00:16:15,039 --> 00:16:15,879
Eat.

189
00:16:28,600 --> 00:16:29,399
Where did you learn?

190
00:16:31,679 --> 00:16:33,960
I told you, at a noodle shop.

191
00:16:39,320 --> 00:16:42,039
I'm just an assistant there,

192
00:16:42,519 --> 00:16:44,120
cleaning and stuff.

193
00:16:44,639 --> 00:16:46,120
Sometimes I also tutor.

194
00:16:53,360 --> 00:16:54,080
Move aside.

195
00:16:55,000 --> 00:16:56,159
I'll handle this.

196
00:16:56,879 --> 00:16:57,799
Go eat.

197
00:16:57,799 --> 00:16:58,519
I'll do it.

198
00:16:58,519 --> 00:16:59,559
How can I choke you if you don't eat?

199
00:16:59,559 --> 00:17:01,080
That's not enough for anyone.

200
00:17:01,480 --> 00:17:02,679
And it's terrible.

201
00:17:03,120 --> 00:17:03,840
Move aside.

202
00:17:06,839 --> 00:17:08,759
Fine, you wash them.

203
00:17:08,759 --> 00:17:09,680
You do the dishes from now on.

204
00:17:09,880 --> 00:17:11,559
With your cooking skills,

205
00:17:12,279 --> 00:17:13,200
the restaurant won't go bankrupt?

206
00:17:15,559 --> 00:17:17,480
The restaurant I worked at in college

207
00:17:18,079 --> 00:17:19,720
was the most popular noodle shop.

208
00:17:22,039 --> 00:17:23,000
Before you joined.

209
00:19:02,839 --> 00:19:03,279
Sit.

210
00:19:17,960 --> 00:19:18,480
Sit.

211
00:20:45,039 --> 00:20:46,759
Wanwan, help me out here.

212
00:20:46,759 --> 00:20:47,480
Wanwan.

213
00:20:47,640 --> 00:20:48,640
What's up, Mengmeng?

214
00:20:50,119 --> 00:20:52,000
Your place suddenly lost power.

215
00:20:52,000 --> 00:20:52,519
I'm just enjoying

216
00:20:52,519 --> 00:20:54,119
the old-fashioned candlelight night.

217
00:20:56,240 --> 00:20:58,200
Your building is too old.

218
00:20:59,200 --> 00:21:00,000
Don't worry.

219
00:21:00,000 --> 00:21:01,119
Check if it's

220
00:21:01,119 --> 00:21:02,160
the switch.

221
00:21:11,920 --> 00:21:13,680
No, the switch is fine.

222
00:21:14,559 --> 00:21:16,759
It might be the wiring.

223
00:21:18,160 --> 00:21:19,200
In that case, Mengmeng,

224
00:21:19,279 --> 00:21:20,400
you can't use electricity anymore.

225
00:21:20,400 --> 00:21:21,519
It's very dangerous.

226
00:21:21,559 --> 00:21:23,799
So, how long will it take to fix?

227
00:21:24,480 --> 00:21:27,160
To fix it, we need to re-check everything

228
00:21:27,160 --> 00:21:28,160
and install new ones.

229
00:21:28,599 --> 00:21:30,839
It might take a while

230
00:21:30,839 --> 00:21:32,119
to get it sorted out.

231
00:21:34,240 --> 00:21:35,039
How about this,

232
00:21:35,599 --> 00:21:36,920
I'll give you the employee discount

233
00:21:36,920 --> 00:21:38,160
from our hotel.

234
00:21:38,319 --> 00:21:39,119
No, no, no.

235
00:21:39,200 --> 00:21:40,440
Your employee discount

236
00:21:40,440 --> 00:21:41,400
is only a few thousand yuan.

237
00:21:41,400 --> 00:21:42,559
I won't take it.

238
00:21:42,680 --> 00:21:44,119
You... you keep it for yourself.

239
00:21:44,519 --> 00:21:45,440
I have a place to stay.

240
00:21:46,440 --> 00:21:46,880
Then...

241
00:21:47,000 --> 00:21:47,920
do you have

242
00:21:47,920 --> 00:21:49,200
any extra candles?

243
00:21:49,200 --> 00:21:50,680
I... I can't find any.

244
00:21:51,160 --> 00:21:52,799
It seems there are no candles left either.

245
00:21:53,279 --> 00:21:54,400
We need to go out to buy.

246
00:21:55,759 --> 00:21:56,960
It's okay. Forget it.

247
00:21:56,960 --> 00:21:58,200
I'll figure it out.

248
00:21:59,319 --> 00:22:00,720
Just text me on WeChat.

249
00:22:01,319 --> 00:22:01,960
Bye.

250
00:22:01,960 --> 00:22:03,720
Okay. Bye.

251
00:22:17,559 --> 00:22:18,279
Mengmeng.

252
00:22:20,119 --> 00:22:21,200
Lu Xixiao.

253
00:22:22,599 --> 00:22:23,920
Lu Xixiao is sleeping.

254
00:22:28,160 --> 00:22:29,119
Who is it?

255
00:22:29,119 --> 00:22:30,160
It's late at night,

256
00:22:30,160 --> 00:22:31,440
can't you check the time?

257
00:22:32,200 --> 00:22:33,039
What are you doing?

258
00:22:33,039 --> 00:22:34,200
Stop making noise.

259
00:22:34,200 --> 00:22:35,079
How can I sleep?

260
00:22:36,599 --> 00:22:37,880
You even touched my hand

261
00:22:37,880 --> 00:22:39,319
while I was asleep.

262
00:22:42,599 --> 00:22:43,160
You...

263
00:22:46,319 --> 00:22:47,519
You were pretending to sleep?

264
00:22:50,079 --> 00:22:50,839
So,

265
00:22:52,000 --> 00:22:52,519
you called me here

266
00:22:52,519 --> 00:22:53,680
to be your servant?

267
00:22:53,680 --> 00:22:55,359
You deserve it.

268
00:22:57,119 --> 00:22:58,039
Apply the medicine yourself next time.

269
00:23:00,000 --> 00:23:00,799
Let's take a walk.

270
00:23:02,440 --> 00:23:03,240
Are you coming?

271
00:23:07,039 --> 00:23:07,839
As you wish.

272
00:23:07,960 --> 00:23:09,200
I've been walking it myself for years.

273
00:23:09,200 --> 00:23:10,359
Let's go, Liu.

274
00:23:12,440 --> 00:23:13,400
I'll continue to walk it myself.

275
00:23:14,559 --> 00:23:15,359
I walk it in the morning,

276
00:23:15,359 --> 00:23:16,000
in the afternoon,

277
00:23:16,000 --> 00:23:17,559
And I walk it in the early morning. Let's go.

278
00:23:25,039 --> 00:23:26,400
Wait for me.

279
00:23:26,960 --> 00:23:29,200
How can a dog walk a dog?

280
00:23:40,440 --> 00:23:41,079
Liu.

281
00:23:41,319 --> 00:23:42,480
Do you have something to say?

282
00:23:42,799 --> 00:23:43,440
Stop.

283
00:23:44,440 --> 00:23:45,240
It says stop.

284
00:23:45,720 --> 00:23:46,319
Liu.

285
00:23:47,400 --> 00:23:47,920
Liu.

286
00:23:50,359 --> 00:23:50,839
Sit.

287
00:23:51,839 --> 00:23:52,279
Sit!

288
00:23:53,119 --> 00:23:53,599
Speak!

289
00:23:54,839 --> 00:23:56,240
It doesn't listen to you at all.

290
00:23:56,519 --> 00:23:57,240
It has something to say.

291
00:23:57,240 --> 00:23:58,319
It's just too shy to say it now.

292
00:24:00,039 --> 00:24:00,599
What?

293
00:24:03,200 --> 00:24:04,119
It says it's thirsty

294
00:24:04,400 --> 00:24:05,279
and wants some milk.

295
00:24:07,279 --> 00:24:07,960
At your service.

296
